info.description:
A library for building, modifying, observing and training 
    Neural Networks. Very richly featured with :
    - standard summing neurons.
    - multiplying neurons.
    - easy adding and destroying neurons and layers.
    - easy access to neuron names.
    - many training algorithms.
    - JIT optimized network compiling.
    - ...
